/span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ukraine" title=3D"Ukraine">Ukra=
ine</a> introduced capital-gains taxes on property sales from 1 January 200=
6.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-94" class=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikiped=
ia.org/wiki/Capital_gains_tax#cite_note-94"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[<=
